As per Friis free space propagation equation, [latex]
W_{r}=\frac{W_{t} A_{e r} A_{e t}}{(\lambda d)^{2}}
[/latex] when [latex] A_{e r} [/latex] and [latex] A_{e t} [/latex] are doubled and [latex] d [/latex] also doubled, [latex] W_{r} [/latex] is same. Hence capacity is also same.

